ferential equation, and therefore, two types of system response are possible. This novel approach of storytelling and a movie script is used to help make the mathematics of lumped system modeling more approachable for students.  aTitle from PDF title page (viewed on February 22, 2015).  a44 0aMathematical models. 0aDynamicsxMathematical models.1 aDecker, Timothy.,eauthor. 0aSynthesis digital library of engineering and computer science. 0aSynthesis lectures on engineering ;v# 24.x1939-523X403University of Alberta Accessuhttp://dx.doi.org/10.2200/S00610ED1V01Y201410ENG024  hUAINzSYNTHDIG  aInternet AccesswLCc1i6813178-1001lINTERNETmUAINTERNETrYsYtE-RESOURCEu3/2/2015xE-BOOKzSYNTHDIG01bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/24006599